column5: hey there. i was invited to go to maxim lake tamagami for the long weekend in sept  . has any one ever heard or better yett  fished this lake . i have a spot i was thinking of going  that weekend butt  the sound of a new lake intersets me .. any one ever fished this  lake  ? anyt info would be appreaciated.. thx tight lines
I haven't heard of it, but I don't think you can go wrong trying out a new lake in the Temagami area....mark it on your calendar, and go nuts!
Temagami, fished there for 30 years+  Where do you intend to fish?

nope never heard of it.  i'm also headed up to temagami in a few weeks to herridge lake.  only 2 ppl on the board have been there, but many say you that can't go wrong anywhere in temagami - pick a lake and catch away.
Hmm Ive never heard of it.....
Not on any maps I have... or I'm lookin in the wrong place!
